    "─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────",
    "WHAT THIS FILE IS",
    "─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────",
    "These are the named political scenario assumptions for the model.",
    "Each scenario defines how much turnout and Democratic support shifts",
    "for voters in each combination of turnout bucket and partisan bucket.",
    "",
    "IMPORTANT — HOW THE NUMBERS WORK",
    "All delta values are stored as decimals.",
    "A raw value of 5 percentage points is stored here as 0.05",
    "A raw value of -3 percentage points is stored here as -0.03",
    "A raw value of 0 is stored as 0.00",
    "",
    "IMPORTANT — DO NOT CHANGE WITHOUT AUTHORIZATION",
    "These are the initial default values set by the research team.",
    "Do not change any values without direction from the research team.",
    "Do not hardcode any of these values inside the engine or component files.",
